{"tid":118832,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"（扶桑美食2）中村屋 雑錦海鮮丼加火炙壽司盒","createTime":"2017-02-13T09:57:15.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-16T07:49:36.000Z","uid":21545,"like":13,"dislike":59,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2d3851ab46265a3a4bc44e22efb3b9dc48d26552","tid":118832,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T09:57:15.000Z","msg":"今日lab 又可以早走<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   所以就決定再去sogo 扶桑美食節食好西 <br />\n以下為戰利品<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雜錦海鮮丼 $198<br />\n火炙壽司盒 $78<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n首先講講個丼 入面有白飯墊底 上面鋪滿咗各式各樣既魚生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  有海膽 池魚 三文魚子 同三文魚 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/491v358.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F491v358.jpg&h=4f798e05&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/43iH123.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F43iH123.jpg&h=08b30569&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n個池魚 充滿魚油香 又甜又爽 一啲都唔腥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n三文魚 就一般三文魚肥同多油香 但肉質較諗 有可能用日本三文魚 亦可能係放耐咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n三文魚子 粒粒飽滿 精塋透亮 咬落去會爆漿 而且佢醃得恰到好處 既辟走魚腥味 亦保留鮮味 醃料如清酒並沒有暄賓奪主 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n海膽 味道鮮美帶甜 而且從其醜陋外表判斷佢並非加拿大海膽 一係日本貨 一係泡菜菜貨大陸貨<br />\n<br />\n而一個丼中不可或缺既白飯 佢選用珍珠米制成既壽司飯 質地較黏但唔太酸 更加帶出飯既甜味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢d配料唔馬虎 豉油同wasabi 都用日木公司貨 酸薑唔太甜 青瓜都夠爽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n跟住就講下個火炙壽司盒 <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/13/173852_fc84a75a7ea9f35b6babeedd73143b4e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F13%2F173852_fc84a75a7ea9f35b6babeedd73143b4e.jpg&h=9b9c3927&s={SIZE}\" /> 食到一半先記得影<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n入面有七款壽司 一樣一舊 包括 油甘魚 吞拿魚（赤身)  平目魚背 帆立貝 赤貝 三文魚 同熟八爪魚 <br />\n<br />\n大部分魚生質素唔錯 <br />\n<br />\n要點名讚下個平目魚背 入口即溶 又香又油 十分滿足<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n沙律醬並非一般千島醬 有加入煉奶同柚子胡椒等調味 所以味道獨特 以咸同酸為主 輔以甜味 同少少辛味作點綴 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n總括而言 好撚貴 但好撚掂 糧頭可以一試<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我仲買咗啲和菓子 今晚食完再寫食評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed0a52a55ed3dea637b5dcb5da086f7cb4dd505e","tid":118832,"uid":9564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T09:58:18.000Z","msg":"check your tg<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e24dac8dd05af45dbbcdcf3e7ef0c9f49b16ab7","tid":118832,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T10:30:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"888734798eca313db4e3fd0d041ced8fbe951783","tid":118832,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T11:18:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a494b9184ac15db217c4eb06d