frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2e5c4c86e479bf603cc6edf9c5290029554300d","tid":118832,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T14:11:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>正常都要用珍珠米啦........</blockquote><br />\n你又啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"978c9797fcde38fd2af852e7956492a2ab1a58ba","tid":118832,"uid":33878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T14:16:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>198咁貴點解唔去定食Doraya<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n想知道佢憑咩賣咁貴</blockquote><br />\n你呢個都咁上下啦<br />\n人地真係有質素保證<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30fdb5e2b15623c72fd5a01ccb789f1a28a04c8e","tid":118832,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T14:19:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>198咁貴點解唔去定食Doraya<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n想知道佢憑咩賣咁貴</blockquote><br />\n你呢個都咁上下啦<br />\n人地真係有質素保證<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁我覺得佢都值$198 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e28016223eec38c2317a7c660ebd29ea0824769","tid":118832,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T14:19:49.000Z","msg":"咩係ust"},{"pid":"25dc284d83c22a4aef56b7e213b23b72494cb0af","tid":118832,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T14:20:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咩係ust</blockquote><br />\nUniversity of science and technology <br />\n我係咪真心咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4226ea86919a78bda7d479416be286f28da99744","tid":118832,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"20